  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial is a prospective, randomized, controlled, multi-center study. Patients
      will be randomized 1:1 to receive either transcatheter aortic valve replacement (TAVR) with
      the Edwards SAPIEN 3 THV or clinical surveillance. Patients will be stratified by whether or
      not they are able to perform a treadmill stress test. Patients who have a positive stress
      test will be followed in a registry to collect data on subsequent treatment and mortality, as
      applicable.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
